\ Logical ops on truthiness. True is -1, false is 0.
\ Any non-zero float (and any non-empty object) is truthy.

\ and
1 1 and . cr        \ -1
1 0 and . cr        \ 0
0 1 and . cr        \ 0
0 0 and . cr        \ 0

\ or
1 1 or . cr         \ -1
1 0 or . cr         \ -1
0 1 or . cr         \ -1
0 0 or . cr         \ 0

\ not
0 not . cr          \ -1
1 not . cr          \ 0
5 not . cr          \ 0
-3 not . cr         \ 0

\ truthiness of non-1 values
42 7 and . cr       \ -1  (both non-zero)
0 0= . cr           \ -1  (0= agrees with not on 0)

\ composition
1 0 or  0 not  and . cr     \ (1 or 0) and (not 0) = -1 and -1 = -1
1 1 and not . cr            \ not (1 and 1) = 0
